<li id="cite_note-38"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-38">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFNuboerCoemansVos_Hzn1995" class="citation journal cs1">Nuboer, J. F. W.; Coemans, M. a. J. M.; Vos Hzn, J. J. (1995-02-01). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://jeb.biologists.org/content/198/2/325">"No evidence for polarization sensitivity in the pigeon electroretinogram"</a>. <i>Journal of Experimental Biology</i>. <b>198</b> (2): 325–335. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1242%2Fjeb.198.2.325">10.1242/jeb.198.2.325</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0022-0949">0022-0949</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9317897">9317897</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20190827032524/https://jeb.biologists.org/content/198/2/325">Archived</a> from the original on 2019-08-27<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2019-08-27</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Experimental+Biology&amp;rft.atitle=No+evidence+for+polarization+sensitivity+in+the+pigeon+electroretinogram&amp;rft.volume=198&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=325-335&amp;rft.date=1995-02-01&amp;rft.issn=0022-0949&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F9317897&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1242%2Fjeb.198.2.325&amp;rft.aulast=Nuboer&amp;rft.aufirst=J.+F.+W.&amp;rft.